author: Karen Kay Matias
text:
Great location with a view of the harboufront sunset!!

Space is not very crowded, always clean and complete with all the equipments I need!
Shower is perfect for those heading office after workout!

Very friendly and accommodating staffs!
Gigi has been very helpful in assisting me from the moment I signed up to sending me regular updates . She even went extra mile in assisting me and my friends who are doing free trial!

author: Mitcher Pang
text:
I can't recommend Anytime Fitness Labrador View enough. This gym truly stands out for two major reasons: the top-notch equipment and the incredible view.

The gym is always clean, well-maintained, and stocked with a fantastic range of modern equipment. Whether you're into cardio, strength training, or functional fitness, they have everything you need. The machines are from great brands and are consistently in working order, which makes every workout session smooth and effective.

But the real game-changer is the view! Working out while looking out over the water and the Labrador area is incredibly motivating. It turns a routine session into a genuinely enjoyable experience. Itâ€™s the perfect way to clear your head and energize your body.

The staff are also very friendly and professional, and the 24/7 access is the ultimate convenience. If you're looking for a gym that will make you want to work out, this is the place.

author: Derrick Tay
text:
Nice decent size and new solid equipment! Also friendly and helpful staff!
However, air circulation is bad and temperature is too warm. The fans and air circulators is just not cooling the place like a proper airconditioner. There are many ceiling cassette aircon but only 1 is switched on.  Please improve on your air conditioning! Much appreciated!

text: A very good gym with great equipment and good staff. We can clearly see that they have really really good staff, they also welcome everyone with a warm smile everyday. Overall this gym is veryy good.
